Q1. What is dark energy?

I think dark energy is the energy that is causing the expansion of the universe. It is a force that is pushing the universe apart. It is also called dark matter.

Q2. What is dark matter?

Dark matter is a type of matter that is not made up of atoms or molecules. It is thought to make up about 85% of the universe.
